# Multiplayer & Anchor Sharing Design (2025-06-04)

## Features
- Anchor sharing as "quantum bookmarks" or "timeline seeds"
- Collaborative and competitive anchor use in multiplayer (combine, contest, remix)
- Anchor trading, discovery, and sabotage mechanics
- Multiplayer Holo Deck: players can visit, merge, or remix realities

## Technical
- Secure, portable anchor serialization for sharing
- Multiplayer sync for anchor state and timeline branches
- Hooks for PvP and co-op anchor interactions
